; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 1033-1035
; Tests the assertion check inside auto transactions.
; When an auto transaction has an 'assert' directive that evaluates to false,
; a parse_error should be thrown.

= /Expenses:Food/
    assert amount > 100
    (Budget:Food)              -1.0

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 12:
While applying automated transaction from "$FILE", lines 6-8:
> = /Expenses:Food/
>     assert amount > 100
>     (Budget:Food)              -1.0
While extending transaction from "$FILE", lines 10-12:
> 2024/01/01 Groceries
>     Expenses:Food              $50.00
>     Assets:Cash
Error: Transaction assertion failed: (amount > {100})
end test
